function addLocation(string name, string description, int32 latitude, int32 longitude, bytes32 geohash)

function getLocationByGeohash3ByIndex(bytes32 geohash3, uint256 index) view returns (tuple(string name, string description, int32 latitude, int32 longitude, bytes32 geohash, bytes32 geohash5, bytes32 geohash3))

function getLocationByGeohash5ByIndex(bytes32 geohash5, uint256 index) view returns (tuple(string name, string description, int32 latitude, int32 longitude, bytes32 geohash, bytes32 geohash5, bytes32 geohash3))
function getLocationByName(string name) view returns (tuple(string name, string description, int32 latitude, int32 longitude, bytes32 geohash, bytes32 geohash5, bytes32 geohash3))
function locations(uint256) view returns (string name, string description, int32 latitude, int32 longitude, bytes32 geohash, bytes32 geohash5, bytes32 geohash3)
